  "title": "Senior Project Manager (Architecture)",
  "description": "<p>Role &amp; Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure design complies with all statutory requirements</li>\n  <li>Managing design development of the project</li>\n  <li>Execute tender procurement</li>\n  <li>On-site construction supervision</li>\n  <li>Procure statutory compliance for TOP and CSC</li>\n  <li>Monitor the making good of defects and final certification</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree from a recognized university</li>\n  <li>Minimum 8 years of relevant working experience</li>\n  <li>good communication skills in English</li>\n  <li>Passion for design, a commitment to continued learning and the desire to innovate</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal skills and the ability to work independently</li>\n  <li>Ability to supervise and manage a team</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with HDB projects is an advantage</li>\n  <li>Contract administration (SIA/PSSCOC forms of contract)</li>\n  <li>Good technical knowledge and strong detailing capability</li>\n  <li>Be familiar with prevailing regulations and codes governing construction and architectural practice</li>\n  <li>remuneration will be commensurate with your experience and qualification</li>\n</ul>",
